  "title": "2024학년도 1학기 신규 및 정기 연구실 안전교육 시행",
  "category": "안내",
  "published_at": "2024-02-21",
  "detail_url": "https://www.dongguk.edu/article/SAFENOTICE/detail/26754614",
  "content_text": "1.\n관련\n:\n연구실 안전환경 조성에 관한 법률 제\n20\n조\n(\n교육\n․\n훈련\n)\n2.\n상기 법에 의거하여\n, 2024\n학년도\n1\n학기 신규 및 정기\n연구실 안전교육을 아래와 같이 시행하오니 기한 내 반드시 이수하여 주시기 바랍니다\n.\n가\n.\n교육명\n: 2024\n학년도\n1\n학기 신규 및 정기\n연구실 안전교육\n나\n.\n대상\n:\n이공계열 학부생\n,\n대학원생\n다\n.\n교육기간\n: 2024.02.22.(\n목\n) ~ 06.30.(\n일\n)\n라\n.\n교육내용\n:\n연구실 안전법\n,\n화학\n,\n전기\n,\n소방\n,\n안전장비\n,\n연구실사고 등 그 밖에 안전관리에 관한 사항\n마\n.\n교육방법\n1) 신규교육 : 종료\n2)\n정기교육\n:\n온라인교육\n-\n연구실안전교육시스템\n(https://edu.labs.go.kr)\n접속 후 원하는 교육 수강\n바\n.\n안전교육 이수시간\n대\n상\n구분\n관련학과\n비고\n신규\n전체\n신규 입학 대학원생\n,\n학부생\n⇒\n모든 학과 동일\n(\n구분 없음\n)\n입학 후\n3\n개월 이내\n2\n시간\n정기\n고위험 학과\n화학과\n,\n물리학과\n,\n건설환경공학과\n,\n화공생물공학과\n,\n기계로봇에너지공학과\n,\n에너지신소재공학과\n,\n시스템반도체학부\n학기당\n6\n시간\n저위험 학과\n수학과\n,\n통계학과\n,\n전자전기공학부\n,\n정보통신공학과\n,\n건축공학부\n,\n산업시스템공학과\n, AI\n융합학부\n, AI\n소프트웨어융합학부\n,\n가정교육과\n1\n년\n3\n시간\n1)\n고위험 : 위험물\n(\n화학물질\n,\n가스\n,\n실험장치 등\n)\n을 사용하는 학과 및 연구기관\n2)\n저위험 : 고위험 학과를 제외한 학과 및 연구기관\n(\n컴퓨터 취급 연구 활동 등\n)\n사\n.\n기타사항\n1)\n성적 반영\n:\n이\n·\n공 계열 학과 및 과목 일부 성적 반영\n2)\n연구실안전관리위원회에서 정한 기준에 따라 제재를 부여할 수 있습니다.\n3)\n문의사항\n:\n관리처 시설안전팀\n(\n내선번호\n☎\n8569)\n붙 임\n: 1.\n관련 법률\n1\n부\n2.\n온라인 이수 안내서\n1\n부\n.\n끝\n.",
  "content_html": "<p>\n\n</p><p><span style=\"letter-spacing:0pt;\">1. </span><span style=\"font-family:함초롬바탕;\">관련 </span>: <span style=\"font-family:함초롬바탕;\">연구실 안전환경 조성에 관한 법률 제 </span><span style=\"letter-spacing:0pt;\">20</span><span style=\"font-family:함초롬바탕;\">조</span><span style=\"letter-spacing:0pt;\">(</span><span style=\"font-family:함초롬바탕;\">교육 </span><span style=\"letter-spacing:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:함초롬바탕;\">․ </span></span><span style=\"font-family:함초롬바탕;\">훈련</span><span style=\"letter-spacing:0pt;\">)</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"letter-spacing:0pt;\">2. </span><span style=\"font-family:함초롬바탕;\">상기 법에 의거하여</span><span style=\"letter-spacing:0pt;\">, 2024</span><span style=\"font-family:함초롬바탕;\">학년도 </span><span style=\"letter-spacing:0pt;\">1</span><span style=\"font-family:함초롬바탕;\">학기 신규 및 정기 </span><span style=\"font-family:함초롬바탕;\">연구실 안전교육을 아래와 같이 시행하오니 기한 내 반드시 이수하여 주시기 바랍니다</span><span style=\"letter-spacing:0pt;\">.</span></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\"><span style=\"font-family:함초롬바탕;\">  </span></span><u><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\"><span style=\"font-family:함초롬바탕;\">가</span></span></u><u><span style=\"letter-spacing:0pt;font-weight:bold;\">. </span></u><u><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\"><span style=\"font-family:함초롬바탕;\">교육명 </span></span></u><u><span style=\"letter-spacing:0pt;font-weight:bold;\">: 2024</span></u><u><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\"><span style=\"font-family:함초롬바탕;\">학년도 </span></span></u><u><span style=\"letter-spacing:0pt;font-weight:bold;\">1</span></u><u><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\"><span style=\"font-family:함초롬바탕;\">학기 신규 및 정기 </span></span></u><u><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\"><span style=\"font-family:함초롬바탕;\">연구실 안전교육</span></span></u></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family:함초롬바탕;\">  나</span><span style=\"letter-spacing:0pt;\">. </span><span style=\"font-family:함초롬바탕;\">대상 </span>: <span style=\"font-family:함초롬바탕;\">이공계열 학부생</span><span style=\"letter-spacing:0pt;\">, </span><span style=\"font-family:함초롬바탕;\">대학원생</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\"><span style=\"font-family:함초롬바탕;\">  </span></span><u><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\"><span style=\"font-family:함초롬바탕;\">다</span></span></u><u><span style=\"letter-spacing:0pt;font-weight:bold;\">. </span></u><u><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\"><span style=\"font-family:함초롬바탕;\">교육기간 </span></span></u><u><span style=\"letter-spacing:0pt;font-weight:bold;\">: 2024.02.22.(</span></u><u><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\"><span style=\"font-family:함초롬바탕;\">목</span></span></u><u><span style=\"letter-spacing:0pt;font-weight:bold;\">) ~ 06.30.(<font face=\"함초롬바탕\">일</font></span></u><u><span style=\"letter-spacing:0pt;font-weight:bold;\">)</span></u></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family:함초롬바탕;\">  라</span><span style=\"letter-spacing:0pt;\">. </span><span style=\"font-family:함초롬바탕;\">교육내용 </span>: <span style=\"font-family:함초롬바탕;\">연구실 안전법</span><span style=\"letter-spacing:0pt;\">, </span><span style=\"font-family:함초롬바탕;\">화학</span><span style=\"letter-spacing:0pt;\">, </span><span style=\"font-family:함초롬바탕;\">전기</span><span style=\"letter-spacing:0pt;\">, </span><span style=\"font-family:함초롬바탕;\">소방</span><span style=\"letter-spacing:0pt;\">, </span><span style=\"font-family:함초롬바탕;\">안전장비</span><span style=\"letter-spacing:0pt;\">, </span><span style=\"font-family:함초롬바탕;\">연구실사고 등 그 밖에 안전관리에 관한 사항</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family:함초롬바탕;\">  마</span><span style=\"letter-spacing:0pt;\">. </span><span style=\"font-family:함초롬바탕;\">교육방법</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family:함초롬바탕;\">    1) 신규교육 : 종료</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"letter-spacing:0pt;\">    2) </span><span style=\"font-family:함초롬바탕;\">정기교육 </span>: <span style=\"font-family:함초롬바탕;\">온라인교육</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"letter-spacing:0pt;\">      - </span><span style=\"font-family:함초롬바탕;\">연구실안전교육시스템 </span><span style=\"letter-spacing:0pt;\">(https://edu.labs.go.kr) </span><span style=\"font-family:함초롬바탕;\">접속 후 원하는 교육 수강</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family:함초롬바탕;\">  바</span><span style=\"letter-spacing:0pt;\">. </span><span style=\"font-family:함초롬바탕;\">안전교육 이수시간</span></p>\n<table style=\"border-collapse:collapse;table-layout:fixed;border-top:none;border-left:none;border-bottom:none;border-right:none;\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width:45px;height:21px;padding:1.41pt 5.10pt 1.41pt 5.10pt;border-top:solid #000000 1.70pt;border-left:none;border-bottom:solid #000000 0.28pt;border-right:solid #000000 0.28pt;background:#f2f2f2;vertical-align:middle;\">\n<p style=\"line-height:140%;text-align:center;word-break:keep-all;text-autospace:none;\"><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\"><span style=\"font-size:9pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:돋움;\">대</span></span><span style=\"font-size:10pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:돋움;\">상</span></span></span></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width:106px;height:21px;padding:1.41pt 5.10pt 1.41pt 5.10pt;border-top:solid #000000 1.70pt;border-left:solid #000000 0.28pt;border-bottom:solid #000000 0.28pt;border-right:solid #000000 0.28pt;background:#f2f2f2;vertical-align:middle;\">\n<p style=\"line-height:140%;text-align:center;word-break:keep-all;text-autospace:none;\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:돋움;\"><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\">구분</span></span></span></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width:385px;height:21px;padding:1.41pt 5.10pt 1.41pt 5.10pt;border-top:solid #000000 1.70pt;border-left:solid #000000 0.28pt;border-bottom:solid #000000 0.28pt;border-right:solid #000000 0.28pt;background:#f2f2f2;vertical-align:middle;\">\n<p style=\"line-height:140%;text-align:center;word-break:keep-all;text-autospace:none;\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:돋움;\"><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\">관련학과</span></span></span></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width:108px;height:21px;padding:1.41pt 5.10pt 1.41pt 5.10pt;border-top:solid #000000 1.70pt;border-left:solid #000000 0.28pt;border-bottom:solid #000000 0.28pt;border-right:none;background:#f2f2f2;vertical-align:middle;\">\n<p style=\"line-height:140%;text-align:center;word-break:keep-all;text-autospace:none;\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:돋움;\"><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\">비고</span></span></span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width:45px;height:40px;padding:1.41pt 5.10pt 1.41pt 5.10pt;border-top:solid #000000 0.28pt;border-left:none;border-bottom:solid #000000 0.28pt;border-right:solid #000000 0.28pt;background:#f2f2f2;vertical-align:middle;\">\n<p style=\"line-height:140%;text-align:center;word-break:keep-all;text-autospace:none;\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:돋움;\"><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\">신규</span></span></span></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width:106px;height:40px;padding:1.41pt 5.10pt 1.41pt 5.10pt;border-top:solid #000000 0.28pt;border-left:solid #000000 0.28pt;border-bottom:solid #000000 0.28pt;border-right:solid #000000 0.28pt;vertical-align:middle;\">\n<p style=\"line-height:140%;text-align:center;word-break:keep-all;text-autospace:none;\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:돋움;\"><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\">전체</span></span></span></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width:385px;height:40px;padding:1.41pt 5.10pt 1.41pt 5.10pt;border-top:solid #000000 0.28pt;border-left:solid #000000 0.28pt;border-bottom:solid #000000 0.28pt;border-right:solid #000000 0.28pt;vertical-align:middle;\">\n<p style=\"line-height:140%;text-autospace:none;\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:돋움;\">신규 입학 대학원생<span style=\"letter-spacing:0pt;\">, </span>학부생</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"line-height:140%;text-autospace:none;\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:돋움;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:0pt;\">⇒ </span>모든 학과 동일<span style=\"letter-spacing:0pt;\">(</span>구분 없음<span style=\"letter-spacing:0pt;\">)</span></span></span></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width:108px;height:40px;padding:1.41pt 5.10pt 1.41pt 5.10pt;border-top:solid #000000 0.28pt;border-left:solid #000000 0.28pt;border-bottom:solid #000000 0.28pt;border-right:none;vertical-align:middle;\">\n<p style=\"line-height:140%;text-align:center;word-break:keep-all;text-autospace:none;\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:돋움;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:-0.4pt;font-weight:bold;\">입학 후 </span><span style=\"letter-spacing:-0.4pt;font-weight:bold;\">3</span><span style=\"letter-spacing:-0.4pt;font-weight:bold;\">개월 이내 </span><span style=\"letter-spacing:-0.4pt;font-weight:bold;\">2</span><span style=\"letter-spacing:-0.4pt;font-weight:bold;\">시간</span></span></span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td rowspan=\"3\" style=\"width:45px;height:137px;padding:1.41pt 5.10pt 1.41pt 5.10pt;border-top:solid #000000 0.28pt;border-left:none;border-bottom:solid #000000 1.70pt;border-right:solid #000000 0.28pt;background:#f2f2f2;vertical-align:middle;\">\n<p style=\"line-height:140%;text-align:center;word-break:keep-all;text-autospace:none;\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:돋움;\"><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\">정기</span></span></span></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width:106px;height:40px;padding:1.41pt 5.10pt 1.41pt 5.10pt;border-top:solid #000000 0.28pt;border-left:solid #000000 0.28pt;border-bottom:solid #000000 0.28pt;border-right:solid #000000 0.28pt;vertical-align:middle;\">\n<p style=\"line-height:140%;text-align:center;word-break:keep-all;text-autospace:none;\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:돋움;\"><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\">고위험 학과</span></span></span></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width:385px;height:40px;padding:1.41pt 5.10pt 1.41pt 5.10pt;border-top:solid #000000 0.28pt;border-left:solid #000000 0.28pt;border-bottom:solid #000000 0.28pt;border-right:solid #000000 0.28pt;vertical-align:middle;\">\n<p style=\"line-height:140%;text-autospace:none;\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:돋움;\">화학과<span style=\"letter-spacing:0pt;\">, </span>물리학과<span style=\"letter-spacing:0pt;\">, </span>건설환경공학과<span style=\"letter-spacing:0pt;\">, </span>화공생물공학과<span style=\"letter-spacing:0pt;\">, </span>기계로봇에너지공학과<span style=\"letter-spacing:0pt;\">, </span>에너지신소재공학과<span style=\"letter-spacing:0pt;\">, </span>시스템반도체학부</span></span></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width:108px;height:40px;padding:1.41pt 5.10pt 1.41pt 5.10pt;border-top:solid #000000 0.28pt;border-left:solid #000000 0.28pt;border-bottom:solid #000000 0.28pt;border-right:none;vertical-align:middle;\">\n<p style=\"line-height:140%;text-align:center;word-break:keep-all;text-autospace:none;\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:돋움;\"><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\">학기당</span></span></span></p>\n<p style=\"line-height:140%;text-align:center;word-break:keep-all;text-autospace:none;\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:돋움;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:0pt;font-weight:bold;\">6</span><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\">시간</span></span></span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width:106px;height:58px;padding:1.41pt 5.10pt 1.41pt 5.10pt;border-top:solid #000000 0.28pt;border-left:solid #000000 0.28pt;border-bottom:solid #000000 0.28pt;border-right:solid #000000 0.28pt;vertical-align:middle;\">\n<p style=\"line-height:140%;text-align:center;word-break:keep-all;text-autospace:none;\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:돋움;\"><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\">저위험 학과</span></span></span></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width:385px;height:58px;padding:1.41pt 5.10pt 1.41pt 5.10pt;border-top:solid #000000 0.28pt;border-left:solid #000000 0.28pt;border-bottom:solid #000000 0.28pt;border-right:solid #000000 0.28pt;vertical-align:middle;\">\n<p style=\"line-height:140%;text-autospace:none;\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:돋움;\">수학과<span style=\"letter-spacing:0pt;\">, </span>통계학과<span style=\"letter-spacing:0pt;\">, </span>전자전기공학부<span style=\"letter-spacing:0pt;\">, </span>정보통신공학과<span style=\"letter-spacing:0pt;\">, </span>건축공학부<span style=\"letter-spacing:0pt;\">, </span>산업시스템공학과<span style=\"letter-spacing:0pt;\">, AI</span>융합학부<span style=\"letter-spacing:0pt;\">, AI</span>소프트웨어융합학부<span style=\"letter-spacing:0pt;\">, </span>가정교육과</span></span></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width:108px;height:58px;padding:1.41pt 5.10pt 1.41pt 5.10pt;border-top:solid #000000 0.28pt;border-left:solid #000000 0.28pt;border-bottom:solid #000000 0.28pt;border-right:none;vertical-align:middle;\">\n<p style=\"line-height:140%;text-align:center;word-break:keep-all;text-autospace:none;\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:돋움;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:0pt;font-weight:bold;\">1</span><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\">년</span></span></span></p>\n<p style=\"line-height:140%;text-align:center;word-break:keep-all;text-autospace:none;\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:돋움;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:0pt;font-weight:bold;\">3</span><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\">시간</span></span></span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td colspan=\"3\" style=\"width:598px;height:40px;padding:1.41pt 5.10pt 1.41pt 5.10pt;border-top:solid #000000 0.28pt;border-left:solid #000000 0.28pt;border-bottom:solid #000000 1.70pt;border-right:none;vertical-align:middle;\">\n<p style=\"line-height:140%;text-autospace:none;\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:돋움;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:0pt;\">1) </span>고위험 : 위험물<span style=\"letter-spacing:0pt;\">(</span>화학물질<span style=\"letter-spacing:0pt;\">, </span>가스<span style=\"letter-spacing:0pt;\">, </span>실험장치 등<span style=\"letter-spacing:0pt;\">)</span>을 사용하는 학과 및 연구기관</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"line-height:140%;text-autospace:none;\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:돋움;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:0pt;\">2) </span>저위험 : 고위험 학과를 제외한 학과 및 연구기관<span style=\"letter-spacing:0pt;\">(</span>컴퓨터 취급 연구 활동 등<span style=\"letter-spacing:0pt;\">)</span></span></span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<p>  <span style=\"font-family:함초롬바탕;\">사</span><span style=\"letter-spacing:0pt;\">. </span><span style=\"font-family:함초롬바탕;\">기타사항</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"letter-spacing:0pt;\">    1) </span><span style=\"font-family:함초롬바탕;\">성적 반영 </span>: <span style=\"font-family:함초롬바탕;\">이</span><span style=\"letter-spacing:0pt;\">·</span><span style=\"font-family:함초롬바탕;\">공 계열 학과 및 과목 일부 성적 반영</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"letter-spacing:0pt;\">    2) </span><span style=\"font-family:함초롬바탕;\">연구실안전관리위원회에서 정한 기준에 따라 제재를 부여할 수 있습니다.</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"letter-spacing:0pt;\">    3) </span><span style=\"font-family:함초롬바탕;\">문의사항 </span>: <span style=\"font-family:함초롬바탕;\">관리처 시설안전팀</span><span style=\"letter-spacing:0pt;\">(</span><span style=\"font-family:함초롬바탕;\">내선번호 </span><span style=\"letter-spacing:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:함초롬바탕;\">☎</span></span><span style=\"letter-spacing:0pt;\">8569)</span></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family:함초롬바탕;\">붙 임 </span><span style=\"letter-spacing:0pt;\">: 1. </span><span style=\"font-family:함초롬바탕;\">관련 법률 </span><span style=\"letter-spacing:0pt;\">1</span><span style=\"font-family:함초롬바탕;\">부</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"letter-spacing:0pt;\">         2. </span><span style=\"font-family:함초롬바탕;\">온라인 이수 안내서 </span><span style=\"letter-spacing:0pt;\">1</span><span style=\"font-family:함초롬바탕;\">부</span><span style=\"letter-spacing:0pt;\">. </span><span style=\"font-family:함초롬바탕;\">끝</span><span style=\"letter-spacing:0pt;\">.</span></p>\n<div id=\"hwpEditorBoardContent\"> </div>",
